    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Queen Margaret Business School is delighted to become a signatory of the United Nations Principles of Responsible Management Education (PRME).</p>
<p>The move means that Queen Margaret Business School is now part of a group of leading business management schools from 90 countries across the world that is committed to building a more sustainable future.</p>]]></Value>
